OL,3,CIsle of Man doctors' dispute over
OL,4,Cafter pay agreement reached with Manx
OL,5,CCare
OL,7,FDoctors on the Isle of Man have
OL,8,Faccepted an offer ending a long-
OL,9,Frunning dispute over pay.
OL,11,FMedics agreed to postpone strike
OL,12,Faction last week, averting what would
OL,13,Fhave been the first walk out in the
OL,14,Fisland's history.
OL,16,FNow Manx Care has said that doctors
OL,17,Fhave accepted an 8% pay increase,
OL,18,Fwhich has been backdated to April 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
