OL,5,CCare
OL,7,FIn a statement it said: "We are
OL,8,Fpleased that this offer has been
OL,9,Faccepted, which puts an end to the
OL,10,Fprotracted pay negotiations.
OL,12,F"Resolution of this matter was enabled
OL,13,Fthrough additional funding provided to
OL,14,FManx Care from the DHSC, for which we
OL,15,Fare grateful.
OL,17,F"It allowed Manx Care, with the
OL,18,Fassistance of MIRS to resolve this for
OL,19,F2023/2024 and 2024/2025, which has
OL,20,Fenabled Doctors on the Isle of Man to
OL,21,Fachieve parity with England.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
