OL,5,CCare
OL,7,F"It is now vitally important that we
OL,8,Freset our relationship with the BMA
OL,9,Fand move forward with a number of
OL,10,Fother critically important pieces of
OL,11,Fwork which secure the sustainability
OL,12,Fof health and care services for the
OL,13,FIsland moving forward."
OL,15,FBritish Medical Association
OL,16,Fnegotiators entered talks with
OL,17,Femployers asking for a 12.6% uplift in
OL,18,Fpay, claiming doctors have faced a
OL,19,F'real terms pay cut since 2008' due to
OL,20,Finflation on the island.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
