OL,7,FThey said that inflation "increased by
OL,8,F56.3%, while the maximum consultant's
OL,9,Fsalary increased by just 27.3% over
OL,10,Fthe same period".
OL,12,FLast week the Isle of Man Health
OL,13,FMinister addressed the issue while
OL,14,Fresponding to a question in Tynwald.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
