OL,7,FSpeaking in parliament, Claire
OL,8,FChristian MHK, said: "I am pleased to
OL,9,Freport that the industrial action plan
OL,10,Ffor this week will now be deferred. In
OL,11,Fview of this Manx care has negotiated
OL,12,Fand offered several options to try to
OL,13,Faddress discrepancies in pay in
OL,14,Fcomparison with their UK counterparts.
OL,16,F"And the agreement has been based on
OL,17,Fthese principles, details, details
OL,18,Fwill follow once the two parties have
OL,19,Fconcluded their deliberations.
